IMAPAccount fastmail
Host imap.fastmail.com
Port 993
User hskim@dilluti0n.com
PassCmd "pass show hskim/fastmail.com | awk '/^app-password-eps:/ {print $2}'"
TLSType IMAPS

IMAPStore fastmail-remote
Account fastmail

MaildirStore fastmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/fastmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/fastmail/Inbox

Channel fastmail
Far :fastmail-remote:
Near :fastmail-local:
Patterns * !"Spam" !"Drafts"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
